description = "[pretext][Log 007] - Unified date 15789.1[/pretext]
[content]
Should we have an emergency and gotta run don't leave [MACHINE_NAME] behind.
The Supercharged Relic is the last tecnology available to do so.
Simply craft a charged Aether Chamber with a diamond and a sync module and a Tesseract.
Be aware that Tesseract are expensive and rare to find. Don't waste it.
[/content]"
